key = "say"
title = "Say"
---
Syntax: {color foreground="white"}say message{/color}
        {color foreground="white"}say @character message{/color}
        {color foreground="white"}say @"character name" message{/color}
        {color foreground="white"}say >adverb message{/color}

To communicate with other characters in the same room as you, use the {color foreground="white"}say{/color} command.
